1.11
log
@Fix previous commit that broke locate.  Unlike printf, print writes a
newline.  So go back to using printf but use an explicit %s format to
make things safe.
@
text
@d3 1
a3 1
#	$OpenBSD: mklocatedb.sh,v 1.10 2003/06/24 23:49:23 millert Exp $
d33 1
a33 1
# $Id: mklocatedb.sh,v 1.10 2003/06/24 23:49:23 millert Exp $
d71 1
a71 1
                awk 'NR <= 128 { printf "%s" $2 }' > $bigrams &&
@


